==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Woden
<hw>Wo"den</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>W⟦omac⟧den</ets>; akin to OS. <ets>W⟦omac⟧dan</ets>, OHG.
<ets>Wuotan</ets>, Icel. <ets>O⟦edh⟧inn</ets>, and probably to E.
<ets>wood</ets>, a. Cf. <er>Wednesday</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Northern
Myth.)</fld> <def>A deity corresponding to Odin, the supreme deity of
the Scandinavians. <xex>Wednesday</xex> is named for him. See
<er>Odin</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

